r bottle for quick access to food and drinks</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">4 IN 1 JAR OPENER: Featuring four different grip sizes, the Beille rubber jar opener or bottle opener can tackle tight plastic or glass jars, mason jar lids and bottles too! You can use the kitchen gadget on 1.5, 2, 2.25 and 3 inch lids</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">DURABLE RUBBER DESIGN: Constructed from strong TPR rubber, this jar opener will stand up to many cooking and baking sessions in your kitchen! Abrasion and chemical resistant, the jar opener provides high impact strength to open the toughest lids; the gadget also features raised grips that give the jar opener even more leverage against those tight lids</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">ARTHRITUS FRIENDLY: Easy to use, simply fit the jar opener over the lid, grip and twist; the rubber handle provides excellent grip and is a great kitchen tool for those with arthritis, hand injuries or lack of hand strength</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t\t<td class=\"attr-right\">SPECIFICATIONS: Dimensions: 9 inch (L); Material: TPR Rubber; Color: Red/Grey; Grip Diameters: 1.5, 2, 2.25 and 3 inches</td>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t  \t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t  </table>\n\t\t\t  </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t  </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t  <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t  <p>&copy; 2024</p>\n\t\t  </div> <!-- /footer -->\n\n\t      </div> <!-- /container -->\n              <div style=\"clear:both\">\n              <table>&nbsp;</table>\n              </div>\n  </body>\n</html> <center><a href=\"https://pages.ebay.com/seller-center/listing/listing-advanced-sellers/third-party-listing-tools.ht